#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:9
msgid "人形机械臂ART3-R7共有四种配置：配置一为单臂，配置二为单臂+控制器，配置三为双臂，配置四为双臂+控制器+分支器。如图2-1、2-2、2-3和2-4所示。到货之后，请依照装箱清单确认装箱物品。"
msgstr ""
"The humanoid robotic arm ART3-R7 has four configurations: Configuration 1"
" is a single arm, Configuration 2 is a single arm plus controller, "
"Configuration 3 is dual arms, and Configuration 4 is dual arms plus "
"controller plus brancher. As shown in Figure 2-1, 2-2, 2-3 and 2-4. After"
" receiving the goods, please confirm the packing list."

