#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:36
msgid "搬运"
msgstr "Handling"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:43
msgid "名称：**危险**"
msgstr "Name: **Danger**"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:45
#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:57
msgid "说明："
msgstr "Instructions:"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:47
msgid "请在机械臂外围设置安全栏，安全栏应具备不易翻越、移动的特点。否则，作业人员可能在机械臂动作时进入区域，导致人员受伤，设备受损。"
msgstr ""
"Please set up a safety barrier around the robot arm, which should be not "
"easy to climb over and mobile. Otherwise, workers may enter the area when"
" the robot arm is in motion, leading to personal injury and equipment "
"damage."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:48
msgid "请明确标识机械臂动作区域。"
msgstr "Please clearly mark the robot arm operation area."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:55
msgid "名称：**警告**"
msgstr "Name: **Warning**"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:59
msgid "使用吊车、叉车等搬运机械臂，必须由持有操作资格证的人员或经公司允许的人员进行。否则，机械臂在搬运中有可能掉落，从而导致事故。"
msgstr ""
"Lifting arms must be operated by personnel holding the corresponding "
"operation qualification certificate or authorized by the company. "
"Otherwise, the lifting arm may fall during handling, causing an accident."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:60
msgid "机械臂安装后，要确保机械臂完全展开时，其腕部工具或工件尖端不会碰触到墙壁或安全栏。否则，可能导致人员受伤，设备受损。"
msgstr ""
"After installing the robotic arm, ensure that when the arm is fully "
"extended, the wrist tool or workpiece tip does not touch the wall or "
"safety barrier. Otherwise, it may cause injury to personnel or damage to "
"the equipment."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:61
msgid "必须将机械臂固定好之后，再接通电源，启动机械臂。 否则，机械臂有倾倒风险，可能导致人员受伤，设备受损。"
msgstr ""
"The robotic arm must be securely fixed before power is applied and the "
"arm is started. Otherwise, there is a risk of the arm tipping over, which"
" may cause injury to personnel and damage to the equipment."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:62
msgid "请不要运行零部件缺失或损坏的机械臂，否则，机械臂误动作，可能导致人员受伤，设备受损。"
msgstr ""
"Do not operate the robotic arm if parts are missing or damaged, as "
"incorrect movements of the robotic arm may cause injury to personnel and "
"damage to the equipment."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:63
msgid "搬运过程中，请避免过度震动和冲击。否则，将影响机械臂性能。"
msgstr ""
"During transportation, avoid excessive vibration and impact. Otherwise, "
"it will affect the performance of the robotic arm."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:65
msgid "人形机械臂ART3-R7产品（含包装）总质量约为12⁓20kg，需多人协作抬起，不建议单人操作，以免发生意外。长途运输前请将机械臂调整至规定的装箱姿势，并使用专用纸箱包装后运输。"
msgstr ""
"The humanoid robotic arm ART3-R7 product (including packaging) has a "
"total weight of approximately 12-20 kg, and needs to be lifted by "
"multiple people. It is not recommended for single-person operation to "
"avoid accidents. Before long-distance transportation, adjust the robotic "
"arm to the specified packing position and transport it after using the "
"dedicated carton box."

