#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:125
msgid "存放场所"
msgstr "Storage place"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:127
msgid "人形机械臂ART3-R7应在-25~60℃，无凝霜环境下存放。"
msgstr ""
"The humanoid robotic arm ART3-R7 should be stored in an environment "
"without condensation, at a temperature between -25~60℃."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:130
msgid "使用环境"
msgstr "Operating Environment"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:131
msgid "安装机械臂的场所需要满足以下条件："
msgstr ""
"The location where the robotic arm is installed needs to meet the "
"following conditions:"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:133
msgid "机械臂运转时，周围温度应在0°C~45°C以内；"
msgstr ""
"When the robotic arm is operating, the surrounding temperature should be "
"within 0°C to 45°C;"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:134
msgid "湿度小、较干燥(工作湿度90%RH，无凝露)；"
msgstr "Low humidity, relatively dry (operating humidity 90% RH, no condensation);"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:135
msgid "不会受到较大冲击和震动；"
msgstr "Not subject to significant impact and vibration;"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:136
msgid "远离灰尘、粉尘、金属粉、腐蚀性气体、易燃性气体、油雾等；"
msgstr ""
"Stay away from dust, powder, metal dust, corrosive gases, flammable "
"gases, oil mist, etc.;"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:137
msgid "远离强磁场、远离电气干扰源等；"
msgstr ""
"Stay away from strong magnetic fields, away from electrical interference "
"sources, etc.;"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:139
msgid "环境温度条件仅为机械臂适用条件。若要在不符合上述条件的场所使用，请咨询本公司。"
msgstr ""
"The environmental temperature conditions are only applicable for the "
"robotic arm. If you need to use it in places that do not meet the above "
"conditions, please consult our company."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:142
msgid "启用"
msgstr "Enable"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:143
msgid "在产品安装和使用前，客户必须针对具体应用场景进行全面的安全评估，重点关注剩余风险因素，并依据本手册对软硬件进行相应的安全配置。首次启动机械臂时，务必密切观察其运动空间，确保无任何干涉或障碍。"
msgstr ""
"Before installing and using the product, the customer must conduct a "
"comprehensive safety assessment for the specific application scenario, "
"focusing on residual risk factors, and perform the corresponding security"
" configurations for the software and hardware according to this manual. "
"When starting the robotic arm for the first time, closely observe its "
"motion space to ensure there are no interferences or obstacles."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:145
msgid "使用机械臂前，请确认机械臂零点姿态与图2-8和图2-9所示姿态一致。若机械臂未移动到图示位置，请咨询本公司。"
msgstr ""
"Before using the robotic arm, confirm that the robotic arm's zero "
"position is consistent with the posture shown in Figure 2-8 and Figure "
"2-9. If the robotic arm has not moved to the position shown in the "
"diagram, please consult our company."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:147
msgid "机械臂在出厂时，已经进行零点标定，所以在日常操作中不需要进行零点标定。但发生下述情况后需要进行零点标定。"
msgstr ""
"The robotic arm has been zero-point calibrated at the factory, so zero-"
"point calibration is not required during daily operations. However, zero-"
"point calibration is needed after the following situations occur."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:149
msgid "更换了关节驱动器或机械臂关节；"
msgstr "Replaced the joint driver or the robotic arm joint;"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:150
msgid "重新安装系统或更换控制器；"
msgstr "Reinstall the system or replace the controller;"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:151
msgid "发生剧烈碰撞后。"
msgstr "After a severe collision."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_begin.rst:153
msgid "机械臂各轴零点标定位置如图2-9所示。"
msgstr ""
"The zero-point calibration positions of each axis of the manipulator are "
"shown in Figure 2-9."

